  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="5010315">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5010315/" class="title-link">虽是选本，内容足够震撼！</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5010315"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/fly_higher/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u14958298-10.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/fly_higher/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">Fly_Higher</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2011-07-03"
      class="main-meta">2011-07-03 22:34:41</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5010315_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  法败则国乱，民怨则国危。  韩非子的法治天下理论，虽然他自己没有看到实行的成果，但是今人读起来，确实足够震撼。  韩非的很多思想确实令人震撼，朴素的语言，深刻的道理。比当今人大教授的“法律是保护弱者的”。牛逼多了。他们要是看了老韩的书，都不会说出这么二的话。

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">1有用 / 1没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
